            <div class="title">
                British And Russian Aircraft (Collision)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-04-06/debates/d05c0df0-88f9-4ed0-9930-f00059420e62/NewMemberSworn" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
